SELECT ca.status, COUNT(ca.Application_ID) AS total FROM cos_application ca WHERE ca.status IN (
'All My Cases', 'OBS Maintenance', 'Rejected', 'Canceled', 'Account Opened' ) GROUP BY ca.status
